}

###
# Test whether a path is readable.
# @note Silent — no error emitted on empty or missing input.
# Renamed from z::file::readable for namespace consistency with z::probe::*.
#
# @param 1: string - Path to test
# @return 0 if readable, 1 otherwise
###
z::probe::readable() {
